            <h2>Factors unique to refugee process impact time</h2>
            <p>
              Several contextual factors shaped the experience and increased the
              time needed to complete the process successfully.
            </p>

            <ul class="body-list">
              <li>Larger families can add additional time per interaction.</li>
              <li>3-way communication slows the conversation flow.</li>
              <li>Some users needed visual cues before interacting with the iPad.</li>
              <li>Room layout influenced confidence and clarity.</li>
            </ul>

