          <section id="pilot-learnings" class="content-section">
            <p class="section-kicker">XXX</p>
            <h2>What we learned from the Pilot</h2>
            <p>
              The pilot revealed that visual cues, room setup, and simplified
              communication patterns were important to building confidence in the
              experience.
            </p>

            <ul class="body-list">
              <li>Parents often signed on behalf of underage children.</li>
              <li>Interpreter mediation changed pacing and comprehension.</li>
              <li>Users needed reassurance before tapping unfamiliar devices.</li>
              <li>Simple symbols supported better understanding.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mini-card-grid">
